    Blazorise Reporting
</DocsPageTitle>

<DocsPageLead>
    Build banded reports that can start from a declarative template, then be edited in the report designer and previewed as HTML or PDF.
</DocsPageLead>

<DocsPageSubtitle>
    Installation
</DocsPageSubtitle>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    Install the <Code>Blazorise.Reporting</Code> package, register the reporting services, and include <Code>_content/Blazorise.Reporting/blazorise.reporting.css</Code> in your host page.
</DocsPageParagraph>

